.TH wxColourPickerCtrl 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxColourPickerCtrl \- This control allows the user to select a colour.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
The generic implementation is a button which brings up a \fIwxColourDialog\fR when clicked. Native implementation may differ but this is usually a (small) widget which give access to the colour-chooser dialog. It is only available if \fIwxUSE_COLOURPICKERCTRL\fR is set to 1 (the default).

.SS "Styles"

.PP
