wxCLRP_USE_TEXTCTRL: Creates a text control to the left of the picker button which is completely managed by the \fIwxColourPickerCtrl\fR and which can be used by the user to specify a colour (see SetColour). The text control is automatically synchronized with button's value. Use functions defined in \fIwxPickerBase\fR to modify the text control.

.RE


.sp
.RS 4
